    "summary": "I recently graduated from the MSc Sociology program, University of Amsterdam. I am an experienced content writer with a passion for research and academia. I\u2019m a curious learner and wear multiple hats at the same time. While my research interests lie in decolonizing sociology, gender and sexuality studies, sustainability practices and research innovation, I find myself interested in interdisciplinary modes of approaching sociological research and incorporating multiple mediums to make academia accessible to all. \n\nMy previous work experience has predominantly been in marketing and copywriting focused on brand identity curation. I am eager to apply my research rigour and academic experience to professional opportunities and am excited to take on new challenges.",
